                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18151025-116-off686 t18151025-116-crimeloc688"></join>, feloniously did falsely make, forge, and counterfeit, a certain bill of exchange
            </rs>, to the tenor and effect following, (that is to say,)</p>
               <p>"868 l. 9 s. 6 d. Sterling,</p>
               <p>"His Majesty's ship Acasta, 27th of March, 1815.</p>
               <p>"GENTLEMAN, Thirty days after sight of this my first of exchange, my second and third of same tenor, unpaid, please to pay unto Mr. 
               <persName id="t18151025-116-person1016">
                  Jonathan 
                  Gaine
               <interp inst="t18151025-116-person1016" type="surname" value="Gaine"></interp>
