                  </persName>
            , or order, the sum of eight hundred and sixty-eight pounds nine shillings and sixpence sterling, for value received in provisions, purchased for the use of his Majesty's ships, Acasta, Newcastle and Leander, as per vouchers, to be transmitted by,</p>
               <p>"GENTLEMEN,</p>
               <p>"Your humble servant,</p>
               <p>"
               <persName id="t18151025-116-person1017">
                  JOHN 
                  TREVARTON
               <interp inst="t18151025-116-person1017" type="surname" value="TREVARTON"></interp>
