                  </persName>
            . I am purser of his Majesty's<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181510250049"></xptr>ship Acasta; that vessel was at Say on the 27th of March. This signature affixed to the bill in question,</p>
               <p>"A. R. Kerr," is not his hand writing.</p>
